how many fires the servants built?

530
00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:31.960
- I build my own fires.
- That's admirable.

531
00:40:33.360 --> 00:40:36.160
I spent six months out there.
beyond the Wall

532
00:40:36.560 --> 00:40:38.680
during the last winter.

533
00:40:39.800 --> 00:40:43.680
Supposed to be a two-week mission.
We heard a rumor Mance Rayder

534
